{"kanda":6,"sarga":19,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"राघवेणाभयेदत्तेसन्नतोरावणानुजः ।विभीषणोमहाप्राज्ञोभूमिंसमवलोकयन्","trans":"When wise Vibheeshana, the brother of Ravana was assured of security by Raghava, he looked around the ground and prepared (to descend).","words":[{"d":"राघवेण:","m":"by Raghava"},{"d":"अभये:","m":"promised security"},{"d":"दत्ते:","m":"given"},{"d":"रावाणानुजः","m":"to Ravana's brother"},{"d":"महाप्राज्ञः","m":"wise"},{"d":"विभीषणः","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"सन्नतः","m":"prepared to"},{"d":"भूमिम्","m":"ground"},{"d":"समवलोकयन्","m":"looked around."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"खात्पपातावनींहृष्टोभक्तेरनुचरैस्सह ।सतरामस्यपरमात्मानिपपातविभीषणः","trans":"Righteous Vibheeshana descended from the sky and fell at the feet of Rama accompanied by his devotees happily (considering it to be inappropriate to come with foot down he came straight down with his body).","words":[{"d":"धर्मात्मा:","m":"righteous self"},{"d":"सः","m":"that"},{"d":"विभीषणः","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"हृष्टः","m":"happily"},{"d":"खात्","m":"from the sky"},{"d":"भक्तेः","m":"devotees"},{"d":"सहा:","m":"accompanied by"},{"d":"अवनिम्","m":"on to the land"},{"d":"पपातात:","m":"descended"},{"d":"रामस्य:","m":"towards Rama"},{"d":"निपपात:","m":"fell on the feet."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"पादयोश्शरणान्वेषीचतुर्भिस्सहराक्षसैः ।अब्रवीच्चतदावाक्यंरामंप्रतिविभीषणः धर्मयुक्तंचयुक्तंचसाम्प्रतंसम्प्रहर्षणम् ।","trans":"Thereafter Vibheeshana and the four Rakshasas who sought shelter prostrated lying at the feet of Rama expressing their duty, duly and placing confidence in Rama who spoke these words showing extreme joy.","words":[{"d":"अथ:","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"विभीषणः","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"चतुर्भिः","m":"and the four"},{"d":"राक्षसैःसह:","m":"along with Rakshasas"},{"d":"पादयोः","m":"by foot"},{"d":"शरणान्वेषी:","m":"who seeks shelter"},{"d":"निपपात:","m":"prostrated falling down"},{"d":"रामंप्रति:","m":"in front of Rama"},{"d":"धर्मयुक्तम्","m":"duly expressing his duty"},{"d":"युक्तंच:","m":"and appropriate"},{"d":"साम्प्रतम्","m":"placing confidence in"},{"d":"सम्प्रहर्षणम्","m":"showing extreme joy"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"these words"},{"d":"अब्रवीच्च:","m":"spoken."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"अनुजोरावणस्याहंतेनचाप्यवमानितः ।भवन्तंसर्वभूतानांशरण्यंशरणागतः","trans":"\"I am Ravana's younger brother. Having been put to shame I came to seek protection from you who are the protector of all beings \" (Vibheeshana said to Rama).\"","words":[{"d":"अहम्","m":"I am"},{"d":"रावणस्य:","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"अनुजः","m":"younger brother"},{"d":"तेन:","m":"having been"},{"d":"अवमानितश्च:","m":"put to shame"},{"d":"सर्वभूतानाम्","m":"all beings"},{"d":"शरण्यम्","m":"protector"},{"d":"भवन्तम्","m":"you are"},{"d":"शरणागतः","m":"came to seek protection."}]},{"v":5,"dev":"परित्यक्तामयालङ्कमित्राणिचधनानिच ।भवद्गतंहिमेराज्यंजीवितंचसुखानिच","trans":"\"Leaving Lanka, my friends and my wealth I came to you. Now my life, kingdom and welfare are at your disposal.\"","words":[{"d":"मया:","m":"my"},{"d":"लङ्का:","m":"Lanka"},{"d":"परित्यक्ता:","m":"leaving"},{"d":"मित्राणिच:","m":"and friends"},{"d":"धनानिच:","m":"even wealth"},{"d":"मे:","m":"my"},{"d":"राज्यम्","m":"kingdom"},{"d":"भवद्गतंहि:","m":"at your disposal"},{"d":"जीवितम्","m":"life"},{"d":"सुखानिच:","m":"for happiness."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"तथ्यतद्वचनंश्रुत्वारामोवचनमब्रवीत् वचसासान्त्वयित्वैनंलोचनाभ्यांपिबन्निव ।आख्याहिममतत्त्वेनराक्षसानांबलाबलम्","trans":"\"On hearing those words (of Vibheeshana) that were soothing to him as if he drank (Vibheeshana's love) with his both eyes, Rama asked Vibheeshana to truly relate the strength as well as weakness of the Rakshasas.\"","words":[{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"तस्य:","m":"that"},{"d":"तत् वचनम्","m":"those words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा:","m":"on hearing"},{"d":"वचसा:","m":"word"},{"d":"एनम्","m":"that way"},{"d":"सान्त्वयित्वा:","m":"soothing him"},{"d":"लोचनाभ्याम्","m":"with both eyes"},{"d":"पिबन्निव:","m":"as if drinking"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"words"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoken"},{"d":"राक्षसानाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"बलाबलम्","m":"strength as well as weakness"},{"d":"मम:","m":"to me"},{"d":"तत्त्वेन:","m":"truly"},{"d":"आख्याहि:","m":"related."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"तथ्यतद्वचनंश्रुत्वारामोवचनमब्रवीत् वचसासान्त्वयित्वैनंलोचनाभ्यांपिबन्निव ।आख्याहिममतत्त्वेनराक्षसानांबलाबलम्","trans":"\"On hearing those words (of Vibheeshana) that were soothing to him as if he drank (Vibheeshana's love) with his both eyes, Rama asked Vibheeshana to truly relate the strength as well as weakness of the Rakshasas.\"","words":[{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"तस्य:","m":"that"},{"d":"तत् वचनम्","m":"those words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा:","m":"on hearing"},{"d":"वचसा:","m":"word"},{"d":"एनम्","m":"that way"},{"d":"सान्त्वयित्वा:","m":"soothing him"},{"d":"लोचनाभ्याम्","m":"with both eyes"},{"d":"पिबन्निव:","m":"as if drinking"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"words"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoken"},{"d":"राक्षसानाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"बलाबलम्","m":"strength as well as weakness"},{"d":"मम:","m":"to me"},{"d":"तत्त्वेन:","m":"truly"},{"d":"आख्याहि:","m":"related."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"एवमुक्तंतदारक्षोरामेणाक्लिष्टकर्मणा ।रावणस्यबलंसर्वमाख्यातुमुपचक्रमे","trans":"Then the Rakshasa (Vibheeshana) having heard that Rama of unwearied action would save him proceeded to speak out about the strength of Ravana.","words":[{"d":"तदा:","m":"then"},{"d":"अक्लिष्टकिर्मणा:","m":"of unwearied action"},{"d":"रामेण:","m":"by Rama"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"उक्तम्","m":"having said"},{"d":"रक्षः","m":"Rakshasa (Vibheeshana)"},{"d":"रावणस्य:","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"सर्वम्","m":"all"},{"d":"बलम्","m":"strength"},{"d":"आख्यातुम्","m":"to speak out"},{"d":"उपचक्रमे:","m":"proceeded."}]},{"v":9,"dev":"अवध्यस्सर्वभूतानांगन्धर्वोरगरक्षसाम् ।राजपुत्रदशग्रीवोवरदानात्स्वयंभुवः","trans":"\"Oh Prince, by virtue of a boon granted by Brahma, the selfborn to the tenheaded Ravana, he cannot be killed by Gandharvas, Rakshasas and by all beings.\"","words":[{"d":"राजपुत्र:","m":"prince"},{"d":"स्वयंभुवः","m":"selfborn Brahma"},{"d":"वरदानात्:","m":"by virtue of a boon"},{"d":"दशग्रीवः","m":"tenheaded Ravana"},{"d":"गन्धर्वोररक्षसाम्","m":"by Gandharvas, serpents or Rakshasas"},{"d":"सर्वभूतानाम्","m":"by all beings"},{"d":"अवध्यः","m":"not possible to kill."}]},{"v":10,"dev":"रावणानन्तरोभ्राताममज्येष्ठश्चवीर्यवान् ।कुम्भकर्णोमहातेजाश्शक्रप्रतिबलोयुधि","trans":"\"My elder brother, the one who is younger to Ravana is a highly valiant one endowed with great prowess. He is Kumbhakarna and equal to Indra in war.\"","words":[{"d":"रावणानन्तरः","m":"younger to Ravana"},{"d":"भ्राता:","m":"brother"},{"d":"मम:","m":"my"},{"d":"ज्येष्ठश्च:","m":"elder's"},{"d":"वीर्यवान्","m":"highly valiant"},{"d":"महातेजा:","m":"of great prowess"},{"d":"कुम्बकर्णः","m":"Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"युधि:","m":"in war"},{"d":"शक्रप्रतिबलः","m":"equal to Indra in strength."}]},{"v":11,"dev":"रामसेनापतिस्तस्यप्रहास्तोयदिवाश्रुतः ।कैलासेयेनसङ्ग्रामेमणिभद्रःपराजितः","trans":"\"Rama You might have heard of Prahastha who the commander in chief of his (Ravana's) army is by whom Manibhadra (Kubera's Commander of Army) was defeated in a comb at in Kailas (the abode of Siva).\"","words":[{"d":"राम:","m":"Rama"},{"d":"येन:","m":"on which account"},{"d":"कैलासे:","m":"in Kailasa"},{"d":"सङ्ग्रामे:","m":"in combat"},{"d":"मणिभद्रः","m":"Manibhadra"},{"d":"पराजितः","m":"defeated"},{"d":"तस्यसेनापतिः","m":"his army chief"},{"d":"प्रहस्तः","m":"Prahastha"},{"d":"ते:","m":"you"},{"d":"श्रुतःयदि:","m":"might have heard."}]},{"v":12,"dev":"बद्धगोधाङ्गुळित्रश्चअवध्यकवचोयुधि ।धनुरादाययस्तिष्टन्नदृश्योभवतीन्द्रजित्","trans":"\"He (Ravana's eldest son) who is possessed of Iguana skin on his hands (to protect), and with a shield that cannot be pierced and who remains unseen in comb at wielding a bow is Indrajith.\"","words":[{"d":"यः","m":"he who"},{"d":"इन्द्रजित्","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"बुद्धगोधाङ्गुळित्रश्च:","m":"possessed with skin of Iguana on his hands"},{"d":"अवध्यकवचः","m":"shield which cannot be pierced"},{"d":"धनुः","m":"bow"},{"d":"आदाय:","m":"wielding"},{"d":"युधि:","m":"in combat"},{"d":"तिष्ठन्","m":"remains"},{"d":"अदृश्यः","m":"unseen"},{"d":"भवति:","m":"will be."}]},{"v":13,"dev":"सङ्ग्रामसमयव्यूहेतर्पयित्वाहुताशनम् ।अन्तर्धानगतश्शत्रूनिन्द्रजिद् हन्तिराघव:।। 6.19.13।।","trans":"\"Raghava Indrajith strikes when caught by a network of foes in war by becoming invisible because of satisfying fire god.\"","words":[{"d":"राघव:","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"शत्रून्","m":"at enemies"},{"d":"इन्द्रजित्","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"हुताशनम्","m":"god of fire"},{"d":"तर्पयित्वा:","m":"by satisfying"},{"d":"अन्तर्धानगतः","m":"goes unseen"},{"d":"सुमयव्यूहे:","m":"when caught by network of foes"},{"d":"सङ्ग्रामसमये:","m":"at the time of war"},{"d":"हन्ति:","m":"strikes."}]},{"v":14,"dev":"महोदरमहापार्श्वौराक्षसश्चाप्यकम्पनः ।अनीकस्थास्तुतस्यैतेलोकपालसमायुधि","trans":"\"Mahodara, Mahaparsva, Akampana are Rakshasas who are like the guards of the world. They are the commanders of his (Ravana's) army.\"","words":[{"d":"महोदरमहापार्श्वौ:","m":"Mahodara and Mahaparsva"},{"d":"अकम्पनः","m":"Akampana"},{"d":"राक्षसश्च:","m":"at Rakshasas"},{"d":"युधि:","m":"in war"},{"d":"लोकपालसमाः","m":"like the guardians of the world"},{"d":"एते:","m":"all these are"},{"d":"तस्य:","m":"their"},{"d":"अनीकस्ध:","m":"commanders in the army."}]},{"v":15,"dev":"दशकोटिसहस्राणिरक्षसांकामरूपिणाम् ।मांसशोणितभक्ष्याणांलङ्कापुरनिवासिनाम्","trans":"\"Thousands of Rakshasas inhabit the city of Lanka living on flesh and blood and changing their form at will.\"","words":[{"d":"कामरूपिणाम्","m":"who change form at their will"},{"d":"मांसशोणितभक्ष्याणाम्","m":"who eat flesh and blood"},{"d":"लङ्कापुरनिवासिनाम्","m":"those residing in the city of Lanka"},{"d":"रक्षसाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"सहस्राणि:","m":"thousands."}]},{"v":16,"dev":"सतैस्तुसहितोराजालोकपालानयोधयत् ।सहदेवैस्तुतेभग्नारावणेनमहात्मना","trans":"\"The unassailable rulers of the world and even celestial beings have been shattered by Ravana accompanied by the Rakshasas.\"","words":[{"d":"सः"